agi
===

This product, "agi", is a rebranded and Russian-localized derivative of
"Fusion" by Runfusion (https://github.com/Runfusion/Fusion), used under the
MIT License. The original copyright notice and the full MIT License text are
retained in the LICENSE file, as required by the license.

Modifications in this fork (agisota/agi):
- Product rebranding from "Fusion" to "agi" on user-facing surfaces and the CLI
  (the internal "@fusion/*" package scope and runtime directories are unchanged).
- Full Russian ("ru") localization of the dashboard and CLI catalogs.
- Russian set as the default UI language (an explicit user choice still wins;
  English remains the source-of-truth fallback).

Upstream project: Fusion (© Runfusion) — MIT License.
